(51,51,51); letter-spacing:0.0000pt; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none; font-style:normal; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; "><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top:11.2500pt; margin-right:0.0000pt; margin-bottom:11.2500pt; margin-left:0.0000pt; text-indent:0.0000pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; mso-pagination:widow-orphan; line-height:17.2500pt; background:rgb(255,255,255); "><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; color:rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing:0.0000pt; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none; font-style:normal; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; background:rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255); ">　　(2)第三至六轮比赛：所有主场俱乐部每场比赛须向中国足协杯赛事委员会无偿提供主席台VVIP门票7张以及主席台区VIP门票40张、一等票(紧邻主席台区域)500张、二等票(紧邻一等票且非角球区域)500张；所有门票应该相互邻近，并在指定区域内；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; color:rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing:0.0000pt; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none; font-style:normal; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; "><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top:11.2500pt; margin-right:0.0000pt; margin-bottom:11.2500pt; margin-left:0.0000pt; text-indent:0.0000pt; padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt ; mso-pagination:widow-orphan; line-height:17.2500pt; background:rgb(255,255,255); "><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; color:rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing:0.0000pt; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none; font-style:normal; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; background:rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading:rgb(255,255,255); ">　　(3)第七轮比赛：所有主场俱乐部每场比赛须向中国足协杯赛委员会无偿提供主席台及主席台区VIP区域50%的门票，一等票(紧邻主席台区域)1000张、二等票(紧邻一等票且非角球区域)500张；所有门票应该相互邻近，并在指定区域内。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-family:宋体; color:rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing:0.0000pt; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none; font-style:normal; font-size:10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt; "><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="margin-top:11.2500pt; margin-right:0.0000pt; margin-bottom:11.2500pt; margin-left:0.0000pt;